result.name: Sakana No Aji

reviews.text:
Quite disappointed for the food served: from the miso soup (like the powdery one you could get from the supermarket), the steamed egg (mostly seasoned watery-like jelly instead of egg), to the main sushi palette (the sea urchin wasn't fresh enough and the sushi rice was neither well made).
The dessert was a disaster. Totally not deserve so many 😋 on Openrice!
Great place for lunch, nice lunch sets, good atmosphere and friendly staff
Quiet corner for decent shushi
Great lunch place! Fresh and high quality food for the price. Not very crowded, lovely environment

Good food
